fields.description:
You cannot append a row on TableView using mobileweb.

Example:
{code}
var win = Ti.UI.createWindow({
  backgroundColor:'white',
});
var tv = Ti.UI.createTableView({
    top : 0,
    left : 0,
    width : Ti.UI.FILL,
    height : Ti.UI.FILL,
    headerTitle:"Hello"
});
var row = Ti.UI.createTableViewRow({
    title : 'List Content Appended'
});
tv.appendRow(row);
win.add(tv);
win.open(); 
{code}

comments.body:
Hello, This is a valid bug, Table view "appendRow" does not work in Mobile Web platform. For Android and iOS it's working fine.


Sample code

{code}
var win = Ti.UI.createWindow({
    backgroundColor : 'white'
});

var table = Ti.UI.createTableView({
    objName : 'table'
});

var row = Ti.UI.createTableViewRow({
    title : 'row',
    color : 'red',
    height : 100
});

table.appendRow(row);

win.add(table);
win.open();
{code}

Tested with SDK 5.0.2.GA, 5.1.0.v20151023172822. Thanks.
